comments: [Observable in enhanced video] Gordon (HOU) splits his feet before releasing his dribble.
Iguodala (GSW) briefly places an arm around Capela's (HOU) front but immediately removes it and does not affect his FOM.
[Observable in enhanced video] Capela (HOU) lifts his pivot foot.
Looney (GSW) makes marginal contact with Capela (HOU).
Capela (HOU) is in the lane for longer than three seconds.
Tucker (HOU) briefly puts his arm around Green (GSW), but immediately slides it off and does not affect his SQBR.
Tucker (HOU) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Curry (GSW) after the release of his jump shot attempt.
Thompson (GSW) cleanly deflects the ball away from Paul (HOU).
Paul (HOU) makes marginal contact with Curry (GSW) on the perimeter.
Tucker (HOU) reaches in and makes contact with Curry's (GSW) arm that affect his SQBR.  Tucker then makes contact with the ball causing it to go into the backcourt, where Curry legally retrieves it.
Gordon (HOU) moves along Curry's (GSW) path and makes marginal contact that does not affect his SQBR.
Gordon (HOU) briefly has his arm around Thompson's (GSW) waist, but slides it off and does not affect his ability to get to the pass.
Gordon (HOU) moves along Thompson's (GSW) path with his arm rested on Thompson's body without affecting his SQBR.
[Observable in enhanced video] Green (GSW) lifts his pivot foot before releasing his dribble.
Tucker (HOU) reaches in and makes marginal contact with Green (GSW) at the start of the drive that does not affect his SQBR.
Tucker (HOU) is established in Iguodala's (GSW) path while setting the screen and does not deliver contact.
Green (GSW) maintains a legal guarding position during Harden's (HOU) driving shot attempt, retreating towards the basket and absorbing the contact.
Tucker (HOU) briefly has his hand on Green's (GSW) side, but slides it off and does not affect his FOM.
Paul (HOU) legally contests Thompson's (GSW) jump shot attempt.
LLB shows Looney (GSW) cleanly blocks Green's (HOU) jump shot attempt.
Tucker (HOU) commits a take foul on Curry (GSW).
Curry (GSW) begins to trip on his own and any contact from Harden (HOU) during the throw-in is marginal.
Gordon (HOU) commits a take foul on Curry (GSW).
Harden (HOU) goes to, but not through Looney's (GSW) body and does not dislodge him from his legally obtained position.
Rivers (HOU) commits a take foul on Curry (GSW).
Looney (GSW) maintains a legal guarding position and Harden (HOU) loses control of the ball on his own.
Paul (HOU) commits a take foul on Iguodala (GSW).
Looney (GSW) places a forearm on Tucker's (HOU) back during the rebound but does not extend his arm and dislodge Tucker from his rebounding position.
Harden (HOU) commits a take foul on Curry (GSW).
